Interface Entity

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ProjectEntity
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Account, AccountGroup, AccountGroupMapping, Branch, Build, LDAPMapping, PredefinedPromotionLevel, PredefinedValidationStamp, Project, PromotionLevel, PromotionRun, ValidationRun, ValidationStamp, ValidationStampFilter

    public interface Entity
    An Entity is a model object that has an ID. The state of this ID will determined the status of this entity:
    • new - the ID is not set.
    • defined - the ID is set.
